  "time_ut": 1658298575,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 3 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc7 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Normal school hours are 3 days a week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has announced that when schools resume next Monday, only Monday, Tuesday and Thursday will be regular school hours, and Wednesday and Friday will be home learning or online learning."
      ],
